<HEADLINE>
SOUR GRAPES: THE FRENCH WINE RESISTANCE VS. ROBERT MONDAVI  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Northern California)   (ATTN. EDITORS: The following 525-word material from The New York
Times Syndicate is for use by clients of The Economist.
Nonsubscribers can use this article only by special arrangement.
