<SLUG> BC-R-IRAN-MEDIA-REVIEW-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
THE FUNNY, BUT FICTIONAL, MULLAH 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating)  (The Week in Review)  
 By SUSAN SACHS   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   CAIRO, Egypt _ In the classic Iranian children's tale, the
