<HEADLINE>
SIMPLE METHOD FOUND TO INCREASE CROP YIELDS 
</HEADLINE>
   (The Science Times)  
(Eds: Also being filed in `a' science file.) 
 By CAROL KAESUK YOON    
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
