<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-21 16:20 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8116 &Cx1f; ttx-z
r e BC-CELEBS-INTERNET-1000(     08-21 0827
