<HEADLINE>
A ROOM WITH A RIVER VIEW
</HEADLINE>
  (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
(Eds: Fact box below. Art available) 
 
 
Story and Photos by ERIC NOLAND  
c.2000 Los Angeles Daily News 
<TEXT>
<P>
   &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL; 
LAUGHLIN, Nev. _ Location is everything. Even here.
</P>
<P>
   In this sweltering gambling town along the Colorado River,
Harrah's hotel and casino is situated at a natural cove, which is
bracketed by buoys that limit watercraft to speeds that don't
