<HEADLINE>
DOGFISH CATCH CURTAILED ALONG EASTERN US 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (a and i coding)   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
 By BETH DALEY  
 c.2000 The Boston Globe  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   BOSTON _ Fishermen from Maine to Florida will be prohibited for
at least six months from catching the spiny dogfish that millions
